  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/01/11/tesla-will-give-model-s-owners-safer-wall-charging-adapters/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/5d54ce1fd65038bb7258a2cf88e09c00/1497836_10152100456002801_1423028655_o.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽然 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Tesla/\">Tesla</a> 已经各位车主的 Model S 送出 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/27/tesla-model-s-software-update-guards-against-faulty-wiring/\">OTA 软件更新</a>，将充电电流波动超出安全范围时的电流自动降低 25%，以减低墙上充电器过热而起火的风险。他们觉得虽然这样已经安全，不过为了向车主提供另一层安全网，所以他们设计了一个改善版的墙上充电器，其内置了热熔断电器，当充电器的温超出一定水平，断电器就会被烧断，以防进一步的升温而引致起火。最后，这个新版充电器将会在几个星期内，开始向现有和新车主送出，等 Tesla 的通知吧。<br />\n<br />\n[图片来源：Tesla]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/10/tesla-will-give-model-s-owners-safer-wall-charging-adapters/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.teslamotors.com/about/press/releases/tesla-provides-customers-upgraded-charging-software-and-adapter\">Tesla</a><br />\n </div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/11/tesla-will-give-model-s-owners-safer-wall-charging-adapters/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20805773/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/11/tesla-will-give-model-s-owners-safer-wall-charging-adapters/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
